const e="/assets/VitaCal-BjXXcBUM.webp",n={title:"Vitacal App – Aplikasi Kesehatan (Beta Test)",slug:"vitacal-app-aplikasi-kesehatan",roles:["UI/UX Designer","Frontend Developer","Backend Developer"],roles_en:["UI/UX Designer","Frontend Developer","Backend Developer"],isActive:!0,gallery:[e,e,e],description:"Aplikasi mobile penghitung kalori dan analisis nutrisi personal menggunakan algoritma Mifflin-St Jeor, terintegrasi Open Food Facts API dan dataset Kaggle.",description_en:"A mobile app for daily calorie calculation and personal nutritional analysis using the Mifflin-St Jeor algorithm, integrated with Open Food Facts API and Kaggle datasets.",longDescription:"Vitacal App adalah aplikasi mobile kesehatan yang membantu pengguna memahami kebutuhan kalori harian mereka secara lebih akurat dan personal. Aplikasi ini menggunakan algoritma Mifflin-St Jeor untuk menghitung BMR, BMI, serta memberikan rekomendasi dan analisis kalori berdasarkan data pribadi pengguna. Proyek ini dikembangkan mulai dari riset UI/UX di Figma, hingga implementasi Frontend menggunakan Flutter dan Backend dengan Flask serta PostgreSQL. Untuk memperkaya fungsionalitas, data pencarian makanan diambil dari dataset publik Kaggle, dan fitur pemindai barcode makanan diintegrasikan langsung dengan Open Food Facts API. Sistem autentikasi menggunakan OTP via Fonnte API untuk akses yang cepat. Fokus utama proyek ini adalah menghadirkan alat pemantau nutrisi yang kompleks secara data teknis, namun tetap memiliki antarmuka yang sangat sederhana digunakan.",imageSrc:e,techTags:["Flutter","Flask","PostgreSQL","Mifflin Algorithm","Open Food Facts API","Kaggle Dataset","Fonnte API","Figma"],timeline:"2025 - 2026",platform:"Mobile Application",platform_en:"Mobile Application",context:"Final Academic Project / Tugas Akhir",context_en:"Final Academic Project / Graduation Thesis",theChallenge:"Memahami asupan kalori harian dan menjaga berat badan ideal merupakan tantangan bagi banyak orang. Sayangnya, banyak aplikasi pencatat kalori di pasaran memiliki antarmuka yang terlalu rumit dan database makanan yang terbatas. Pengguna sering kali merasa kesulitan dan kehilangan motivasi saat harus memasukkan data makanan kemasan yang mereka konsumsi sehari-hari secara manual.",theChallenge_en:"Understanding daily calorie intake and maintaining an ideal weight is a challenge for many. Unfortunately, many calorie tracking apps on the market have interfaces that are too complex and food databases that are too limited. Users often struggle and lose motivation when they have to manually log packaged foods they consume daily.",theSolution:"Pendekatan Vitacal App berfokus pada personalisasi pengguna dan kemudahan input data. Mengandalkan algoritma <strong>Mifflin-St Jeor</strong> yang teruji klinis, aplikasi membagi sistem menjadi Frontend Flutter yang responsif dan Backend Flask. Untuk mengatasi hambatan pencatatan, sistem menarik data dari dataset publik Kaggle untuk pencarian makanan lokal, dan mengintegrasikan Open Food Facts API agar pengguna cukup melakukan scan barcode pada makanan kemasan tanpa harus mengetik manual.",theSolution_en:"The Vitacal App approach focuses on user personalization and ease of data entry. Relying on the clinically proven <strong>Mifflin-St Jeor</strong> algorithm, the app splits the system into a responsive Flutter frontend and a Flask backend. To address logging friction, the system pulls data from a public Kaggle dataset for local food searches, and integrates the Open Food Facts API so users can simply scan barcodes on packaged foods instead of typing manually.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Personalisasi & Analisis Kalori",desc:"Menghitung batas kalori harian, BMI, dan analisis riwayat berat badan secara personal dan presisi menggunakan algoritma Mifflin."},{title:"Smart Barcode Scanner",desc:"Integrasi dengan Open Food Facts API untuk mengenali dan melacak nutrisi makanan kemasan secara instan hanya dengan memindai barcode."},{title:"Pencarian Makanan Komprehensif",desc:"Database pencarian makanan yang kaya dan akurat, diolah langsung dari dataset nutrisi publik Kaggle."},{title:"Otentikasi OTP WhatsApp",desc:"Sistem login dan registrasi yang mulus, aman, dan tanpa password menggunakan nomor WhatsApp melalui integrasi Fonnte API."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Personalization & Calorie Analysis",desc:"Calculates daily calorie limits, BMI, and analyzes weight history precisely using the Mifflin algorithm."},{title:"Smart Barcode Scanner",desc:"Integration with the Open Food Facts API to instantly identify and track packaged food nutrition by scanning barcodes."},{title:"Comprehensive Food Search",desc:"Rich and accurate food search database, processed directly from Kaggle public nutrition datasets."},{title:"WhatsApp OTP Authentication",desc:"Seamless, secure, passwordless registration and login using WhatsApp numbers integrated via Fonnte API."}],theImpact:"Aplikasi ini berhasil menghadirkan solusi pemantauan gizi yang sangat praktis. Integrasi API pihak ketiga (Kaggle & Open Food Facts) secara signifikan memangkas waktu proses logging makanan bagi pengguna, menjadikan aplikasi ini tidak sekadar prototipe teoretis, melainkan produk fungsional yang siap memecahkan masalah diet di dunia nyata.",theImpact_en:"This application successfully delivers a highly practical nutritional monitoring solution. Third-party API integrations (Kaggle & Open Food Facts) significantly reduced food logging time for users, making the app not just a theoretical prototype, but a functional product ready to solve real-world dietary challenges.",projectUrl:"https://github.com/ariyoaziz/vitacal_app"},i="/assets/semesta-kecil-BX4zMtNq.webp",t={title:"Pameran Foto – Semesta Kecil",title_en:"Photography Exhibition – Semesta Kecil",slug:"pameran-foto-semesta-kecil",isActive:!1,roles:["Photographer","Exhibitor"],roles_en:["Photographer","Exhibitor"],description:"Karya fotografi bertema narasi kehidupan dan ruang pribadi yang dipamerkan dalam event fotografi Semesta Kecil tahun 2025.",description_en:"Photography work themed around life narratives and personal spaces exhibited in the 'Semesta Kecil' event in 2025.",imageSrc:i,techTags:["Photography","Event","Exhibition"],timeline:"2025",timeline_en:"2025",platform:"Exhibition / Physical",platform_en:"Exhibition / Physical",context:"Karya Pameran Fotografi",context_en:"Photography Exhibition Work",projectUrl:"https://www.instagram.com/p/DMCtoh9zcL7/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&igsh=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==",theChallenge:"Bagaimana cara menangkap makna mendalam dari hal-hal yang sering diabaikan dalam keseharian? Tantangan utamanya adalah mengkomunikasikan cerita dan emosi melalui ruang pribadi dan objek-objek sederhana tanpa menggunakan narasi teks yang panjang.",theChallenge_en:"How to capture deep meaning from things often ignored in daily life? The main challenge was to communicate stories and emotions through personal spaces and simple objects without using long text narratives.",theSolution:"Melalui pendekatan fotografi dokumenter dan <em>fine art</em>, saya memfokuskan lensa pada detail-detail kecil—sudut ruangan, pencahayaan alami yang masuk dari jendela, hingga letak barang sehari-hari. Komposisi diatur sedemikian rupa untuk menciptakan kesan intim dan personal.",theSolution_en:"Through a documentary and fine art photography approach, I focused my lens on small details—room corners, natural light coming from windows, and the placement of daily items. The composition was arranged to create an intimate and personal impression.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Eksplorasi Visual",desc:"Pendekatan visual yang menitikberatkan pada pencahayaan dan tekstur benda sehari-hari."},{title:"Storytelling Tanpa Kata",desc:"Membangun narasi emosional hanya dengan komposisi gambar dan ruang."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Visual Exploration",desc:"A visual approach focusing on lighting and the texture of everyday objects."},{title:"Wordless Storytelling",desc:"Building emotional narratives solely with image and space composition."}],theImpact:"Karya ini berhasil dipamerkan dalam event fotografi <strong>Semesta Kecil 2025</strong>. Pameran ini mengundang audiens untuk sejenak berhenti, merenung, dan melihat kembali keindahan serta kehangatan yang ada di sekitar mereka setiap harinya.",theImpact_en:"This work was successfully exhibited in the <strong>Semesta Kecil 2025</strong> photography event. The exhibition invited the audience to stop for a moment, reflect, and see the beauty and warmth surrounding them every day."},s="/assets/frameflow-D2wu_GtD.png",r={title:"FrameFlow – Solusi Proofing Foto Modern (Beta Test)",title_en:"FrameFlow – Modern Photo Proofing Solution (Beta Test)",slug:"frameflow",isActive:!0,roles:["UI/UX Designer","Frontend Developer"],roles_en:["UI/UX Designer","Frontend Developer"],description:"Platform delivery foto instan yang mengintegrasikan Google Drive dan WhatsApp untuk mempermudah klien memilih foto favorit tanpa ribet.",description_en:"An instant photo delivery platform integrating Google Drive and WhatsApp to simplify the photo selection process for clients.",longDescription:"FrameFlow adalah solusi proofing foto modern yang dirancang khusus untuk fotografer (Wedding, Portrait, Event, Commercial). Aplikasi ini mempercepat proses pengiriman foto ke klien. Cukup hubungkan Google Drive, buat galeri dalam hitungan detik, dan biarkan klien memilih foto favorit mereka secara interaktif. Hasil pilihan klien akan otomatis dikirimkan ke WhatsApp Anda, menghilangkan keribetan dan miskomunikasi dalam proses seleksi foto. Proyek ini masih dalam tahap beta test.",longDescription_en:"FrameFlow is a modern photo proofing solution designed specifically for photographers (Wedding, Portrait, Event, Commercial). This app speeds up the photo delivery process to clients. Simply connect Google Drive, create a gallery in seconds, and let clients choose their favorite photos interactively. The client's selections will automatically be sent to your WhatsApp, eliminating hassle and miscommunication in the photo selection process. This project is currently in the beta test stage.",imageSrc:s,techTags:["Frontend","Web App","UI/UX Design","Beta Test"],timeline:"2025",timeline_en:"2025",platform:"Web Application",platform_en:"Web Application",context:"Personal Project / Eksplorasi Frontend",context_en:"Personal Project / Frontend Exploration",projectUrl:"https://frameflow-navy.vercel.app/"},o="/assets/my_v3-CGi-phk7.png",l={title:"Website Pribadi v3",title_en:"Personal Website v3",slug:"website-pribadi-v3",isActive:!0,roles:["Frontend Developer","UI Designer"],roles_en:["Frontend Developer","UI/UX Designer"],description:"Website portofolio pribadi modern dengan fitur filter proyek dan dark mode. Dibangun secara responsif menggunakan Vue 3, Vite, dan Tailwind CSS.",description_en:"A modern personal portfolio website featuring project filtering and dark mode. Built responsively using Vue 3, Vite, and Tailwind CSS.",longDescription:"Website Pribadi v3 merupakan pengembangan terbaru dari versi sebelumnya dengan fokus pada peningkatan desain visual, performa, dan pengalaman pengguna yang lebih matang. Website ini dibangun menggunakan Vue 3 sebagai framework utama, Vite sebagai build tool modern, serta Tailwind CSS untuk styling yang responsif. Fitur tambahan seperti dark mode dan sistem filter proyek mempermudah pengunjung dalam menavigasi konten portofolio secara interaktif.",longDescription_en:"Personal Website v3 is the latest evolution of my portfolio, focusing on enhancing visual design, performance, and delivering a more polished user experience. The website is built using Vue 3 as the primary framework, Vite as a modern build tool, and Tailwind CSS for responsive styling. Additional features like dark mode and a project filtering system enable visitors to explore my portfolio content interactively.",imageSrc:o,techTags:["Frontend","Vue.js","Vite","Tailwind CSS","Responsive Design","Personal Website"],timeline:"2026",timeline_en:"2026",platform:"Web Application",platform_en:"Web Application",context:"Personal Project",context_en:"Personal Project",projectUrl:"https://ariyoaziz.github.io/"},m="/assets/my_v1-D5io4I0R.webp",d={title:"Website Pribadi v1",title_en:"Personal Website v1",slug:"website-pribadi-v1",isActive:!1,roles:["Frontend Developer","UI Designer"],roles_en:["Frontend Developer","UI Designer"],description:"Versi awal website portofolio pribadi yang dibuat menggunakan React untuk menampilkan informasi dasar serta eksplorasi komponen frontend.",description_en:"The initial version of my personal portfolio website built using React. Focused on delivering basic information and exploring frontend components.",imageSrc:m,techTags:["Frontend","React","JavaScript","Personal Website"],timeline:"Dikerjakan waktu kuliah (Awal Pembelajaran)",timeline_en:"Developed during college (Early Learning)",platform:"Web Application",platform_en:"Web Application",context:"Personal Project / Eksplorasi Frontend",context_en:"Personal Project / Frontend Exploration",projectUrl:"https://github.com/ariyoaziz/profil",theChallenge:"Sebagai seorang mahasiswa yang baru terjun ke dunia pengembangan <em>frontend</em>, saya membutuhkan sebuah platform untuk memamerkan proyek sekaligus sebagai wadah untuk belajar framework React dari nol. Tantangannya adalah merancang arsitektur aplikasi pertama yang rapi dan responsif.",theChallenge_en:"As a student newly entering the world of frontend development, I needed a platform to showcase projects while also learning the React framework from scratch. The challenge was to design a clean and responsive first application architecture.",theSolution:"Saya membangun portofolio ini menggunakan React.js. Fokus utamanya adalah memahami siklus hidup komponen, <em>state management</em> sederhana, dan cara menstrukturkan file proyek frontend. Desain dibuat cukup sederhana untuk memastikan fondasi kode dapat dipahami dengan baik.",theSolution_en:"I built this portfolio using React.js. The main focus was understanding the component lifecycle, simple state management, and how to structure a frontend project file. The design was kept simple to ensure the code foundation could be well understood.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Komponen Reusable",desc:"Menggunakan komponen React untuk elemen UI yang berulang seperti kartu proyek."},{title:"Informasi Profil",desc:"Halaman dinamis yang merangkum pengalaman belajar dan portofolio awal."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Reusable Components",desc:"Using React components for repeating UI elements like project cards."},{title:"Profile Info",desc:"A dynamic page summarizing my early learning journey and portfolio."}],theImpact:"Website v1 ini menjadi batu loncatan yang sangat penting. Melalui proyek ini, pemahaman saya tentang JavaScript modern dan React meningkat drastis, yang pada akhirnya memuluskan langkah saya untuk membangun versi-versi website portofolio yang lebih kompleks di masa depan.",theImpact_en:"This Website v1 was a crucial stepping stone. Through this project, my understanding of modern JavaScript and React increased dramatically, which ultimately smoothed my path to building more complex portfolio websites in the future."},g="/assets/EcoFood-Bc3qzYfs.webp",u={title:"EcoFood – Aplikasi Pemesanan Makanan",title_en:"EcoFood – Food Ordering App",slug:"ecofood-aplikasi-pemesanan-makanan",isActive:!1,roles:["Fullstack Developer","UI/UX Designer"],roles_en:["Fullstack Developer","UI/UX Designer"],description:"Aplikasi mobile pemesanan makanan dengan autentikasi OTP dan pembayaran online, dibangun menggunakan Flutter, Flask, Fonnte API, dan Midtrans.",description_en:"A mobile app for ordering food, featuring OTP (Fonnte API) and Midtrans payment integration. Frontend built with Flutter, backend with Flask.",imageSrc:g,techTags:["Mobile App","Flutter","Flask","Fonnte API","Midtrans","UI/UX Design"],timeline:"Dikerjakan waktu kuliah",timeline_en:"Developed during college",platform:"Mobile Application",platform_en:"Mobile Application",context:"Academic Project",context_en:"Academic Project",projectUrl:"https://github.com/ariyoaziz/ecofood",theChallenge:"Membangun sistem pemesanan makanan digital end-to-end yang tidak hanya menampilkan antarmuka pesanan, tetapi juga mampu menangani autentikasi pengguna secara aman dan memproses pembayaran secara langsung tanpa harus keluar dari ekosistem aplikasi.",theChallenge_en:"Building an end-to-end digital food ordering system that not only displays order screens, but also handles secure user authentication and processes payments directly within the app's ecosystem without requiring users to leave it.",theSolution:"Aplikasi ini memadukan Flutter di sisi frontend untuk UI yang <em>smooth</em> dan responsif, serta Flask di backend untuk mengatur logika bisnis. Saya mengintegrasikan Fonnte API untuk pengiriman OTP via WhatsApp agar login lebih praktis, serta payment gateway Midtrans untuk simulasi transaksi yang nyata.",theSolution_en:"This application combines Flutter on the frontend for a smooth and responsive UI, and Flask on the backend to manage business logic. I integrated the Fonnte API for OTP delivery via WhatsApp for a more practical login experience, and the Midtrans payment gateway for realistic transaction simulation.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Autentikasi OTP WhatsApp",desc:"Login dan registrasi yang cepat tanpa perlu menghafal password."},{title:"Integrasi Midtrans",desc:"Mendukung simulasi berbagai metode pembayaran digital dengan aman."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"WhatsApp OTP Authentication",desc:"Fast login and registration without the need to remember passwords."},{title:"Midtrans Integration",desc:"Supports safe simulation of various digital payment methods."}],theImpact:"Proyek ini berhasil mendemonstrasikan integrasi API pihak ketiga (Fonnte & Midtrans) dalam satu siklus aplikasi. Ini menjadi bukti nyata pemahaman saya mengenai arsitektur <em>client-server</em> dan pengelolaan transaksi dalam aplikasi mobile.",theImpact_en:"This project successfully demonstrated the integration of third-party APIs (Fonnte & Midtrans) in a single application lifecycle. It stands as clear proof of my understanding of client-server architecture and transaction management in mobile applications."},p="/assets/Cuaca-CN9wpQcT.webp",c={title:"CuacaQu – Aplikasi Info Cuaca",title_en:"CuacaQu – Weather Info App",slug:"cuacaqu-aplikasi-info-cuaca",isActive:!1,roles:["Mobile Developer"],roles_en:["Mobile Developer"],description:"Aplikasi Flutter untuk menampilkan informasi cuaca real-time menggunakan OpenWeather API dengan arsitektur BLoC untuk manajemen state.",description_en:"A Flutter app displaying real-time weather forecasts using the OpenWeather API. Uses BLoC architecture for state management.",imageSrc:p,techTags:["Mobile App","Flutter","OpenWeather API","BLoC","UI/UX Design"],timeline:"Dikerjakan waktu kuliah",timeline_en:"Developed during college",platform:"Mobile Application",platform_en:"Mobile Application",context:"Latihan & Eksplorasi Flutter",context_en:"Flutter Practice & Exploration",projectUrl:"https://github.com/ariyoaziz/cuacaqu",theChallenge:"Saat mengelola aplikasi yang datanya berubah-ubah secara <em>real-time</em> seperti aplikasi cuaca, penggunaan <em>state management</em> bawaan seringkali membuat struktur kode menjadi kacau dan sulit dikembangkan (spaghetti code).",theChallenge_en:"When managing an app with dynamically changing real-time data like weather forecasts, using default state management often leads to messy code that is difficult to scale (spaghetti code).",theSolution:"Saya merancang CuacaQu dengan menerapkan arsitektur <strong>BLoC (Business Logic Component)</strong>. Data diambil dari OpenWeather API, kemudian dikelola melalui <em>stream</em> oleh BLoC untuk memisahkan logika pengambilan data dengan kode antarmuka (UI).",theSolution_en:"I designed CuacaQu by implementing the <strong>BLoC (Business Logic Component)</strong> architecture. Data is fetched from the OpenWeather API and managed via streams by BLoC, separating business logic from the UI code.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Live Weather Data",desc:"Mengambil data suhu, kelembapan, dan kondisi cuaca terkini via OpenWeather API."},{title:"BLoC Pattern",desc:"Implementasi arsitektur bersih untuk memisahkan logika bisnis dari UI."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Live Weather Data",desc:"Fetches current temperature, humidity, and weather conditions via the OpenWeather API."},{title:"BLoC Pattern",desc:"Implementation of a clean architecture to isolate business logic from UI rendering."}],theImpact:"Aplikasi ini berjalan dengan sangat efisien dan mudah dikembangkan lebih lanjut. Melalui proyek ini, fondasi pemahaman saya mengenai <em>State Management</em> tingkat lanjut di Flutter (BLoC) terbentuk dengan sangat kuat.",theImpact_en:"The app runs highly efficiently and is easy to expand. Through this project, my foundation in advanced state management in Flutter (BLoC) was strongly established."},h="/assets/TiketBioskop-CgQB3mhx.webp",k={title:"CineHub – Tiket Bioskop Online",title_en:"CineHub – Online Movie Tickets",slug:"cinehub-tiket-bioskop-online",isActive:!1,roles:["Mobile Developer","UI/UX Designer"],roles_en:["Mobile Developer","UI/UX Designer"],description:"Aplikasi mobile untuk memesan tiket bioskop secara online dengan fitur daftar film, jadwal tayang, dan pemilihan kursi.",description_en:"A movie ticket booking app featuring a movie list, showtimes, and seat selection. Built using Flutter as a personal project.",imageSrc:h,techTags:["Mobile App","Flutter","Dart","UI/UX Design"],timeline:"Dikerjakan waktu kuliah",timeline_en:"Developed during college",platform:"Mobile Application",platform_en:"Mobile Application",context:"Latihan & Eksplorasi Mobile UI",context_en:"Mobile UI Practice & Exploration",projectUrl:"https://github.com/ariyoaziz/cinehub",theChallenge:"Membuat antarmuka interaktif untuk sistem pemesanan bioskop memerlukan logika yang rumit di bagian <em>frontend</em>, terutama saat membangun fitur pemilihan kursi yang dinamis di mana pengguna bisa memilih, membatalkan, dan melihat kursi yang sudah terisi.",theChallenge_en:"Creating an interactive interface for a cinema booking system requires complex frontend logic, especially when building a dynamic seat selection feature where users can select, cancel, and view occupied seats.",theSolution:"Saya menggunakan Flutter untuk merancang UI yang responsif. Logika pemilihan kursi dibuat menggunakan GridView yang dikombinasikan dengan <em>state management</em> lokal untuk merender status kursi (kosong, dipilih, atau penuh) secara langsung (<em>real-time feedback</em>).",theSolution_en:"I used Flutter to design a responsive UI. The seat selection logic was created using GridView combined with local state management to render seat statuses (empty, selected, or occupied) in real-time.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Interactive Seat Selection",desc:"Pemilihan kursi bioskop secara dinamis dengan visualisasi yang jelas."},{title:"Movie Schedules",desc:"Menampilkan daftar film yang sedang tayang beserta jadwal studionya."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Interactive Seat Selection",desc:"Dynamic cinema seat selection with clear visual representation."},{title:"Movie Schedules",desc:"Displays now showing movies along with their studio schedules."}],theImpact:"Proyek ini berhasil mensimulasikan pengalaman pemesanan tiket bioskop yang mulus dan interaktif. Ini sangat melatih kepekaan saya terhadap UI/UX interaktif pada platform mobile.",theImpact_en:"This project successfully simulated a seamless and interactive movie ticket booking experience. It greatly sharpened my sensitivity toward interactive UI/UX on mobile platforms."},b="/assets/game-react-1SrzZZBF.webp",y={title:"Mini Game dengan React",title_en:"Mini Game with React",slug:"mini-game-dengan-react",isActive:!1,roles:["Frontend Developer"],roles_en:["Frontend Developer"],description:"Proyek mini game interaktif menggunakan React untuk mempelajari komponen, state management, dan event handling.",description_en:"An interactive mini-game project using React. Created to deepen basic understanding of components, state, and event handling.",imageSrc:b,techTags:["Frontend","React","JavaScript"],timeline:"Dikerjakan waktu kuliah",timeline_en:"Developed during college",platform:"Web Application",platform_en:"Web Application",context:"Personal Project / Latihan",context_en:"Personal Project / Practice",projectUrl:"https://github.com/ariyoaziz/Rect_game",theChallenge:"Memahami bagaimana aliran data (<em>data flow</em>) dan perubahan antarmuka bekerja di dalam framework React, terutama ketika berhubungan dengan input dinamis dari pengguna secara terus menerus (interaksi game).",theChallenge_en:"Understanding how data flow and interface updates work in the React framework, especially when dealing with continuous dynamic user input (game interactions).",theSolution:"Saya membangun proyek <em>mini game</em> ini dengan mengandalkan fitur React dasar seperti <code>useState</code> dan <code>useEffect</code>. Fokusnya adalah memastikan setiap interaksi (seperti klik) segera memperbarui <em>state</em> aplikasi tanpa menyebabkan masalah <em>re-rendering</em> yang tidak perlu.",theSolution_en:"I built this mini game project relying on basic React features like <code>useState</code> and <code>useEffect</code>. The focus was to ensure that every interaction (like clicks) instantly updates the application state without causing unnecessary re-rendering issues.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Dynamic State Management",desc:"Perubahan skor dan status game secara langsung berkat pengelolaan state React yang efisien."},{title:"Event Handling",desc:"Respons interaktif terhadap aksi klik pengguna pada komponen secara real-time."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Dynamic State Management",desc:"Live score and game state updates thanks to efficient React state management."},{title:"Event Handling",desc:"Real-time interactive responses to user click actions on components."}],theImpact:"Proyek sederhana ini sukses memberikan saya pemahaman inti (<em>core fundamental</em>) dari ekosistem React, seperti props dan state, yang sangat berguna ketika mengerjakan aplikasi berskala besar nantinya.",theImpact_en:"This simple project successfully gave me the core fundamentals of the React ecosystem, such as props and state, which are highly useful when working on large-scale applications later."},f="/assets/login_sederhana-BwE2fPcr.webp",v={title:"Aplikasi Login Flutter",title_en:"Flutter Login App",slug:"aplikasi-login-flutter",isActive:!1,roles:["Mobile Developer"],roles_en:["Mobile Developer"],description:"Aplikasi login sederhana menggunakan Flutter sebagai latihan dasar autentikasi dan navigasi halaman.",description_en:"A simple login application using Flutter as a basic exercise in authentication and page navigation.",imageSrc:f,techTags:["Mobile App","Flutter","Dart"],timeline:"Dikerjakan waktu kuliah",timeline_en:"Developed during college",platform:"Mobile Application",platform_en:"Mobile Application",context:"Latihan Dasar Flutter",context_en:"Basic Flutter Practice",projectUrl:"https://github.com/ariyoaziz/aplikasi_login-sederhana-",theChallenge:"Sebagai pengembang aplikasi mobile pemula, salah satu rintangan pertama adalah memahami bagaimana cara berpindah halaman (<em>routing</em>) dan menangani validasi input pengguna dari form secara aman dan efisien.",theChallenge_en:"As a beginner mobile application developer, one of the first hurdles is understanding how to navigate between pages (<em>routing</em>) and handle validation of user inputs from forms securely and efficiently.",theSolution:"Saya membuat simulasi form login dan registrasi menggunakan Flutter. Proses ini melibatkan implementasi <code>TextEditingController</code> untuk menangkap input, menambahkan logika validasi bawaan (seperti mengecek email yang kosong atau password yang kurang panjang), serta menggunakan sistem <code>Navigator</code> bawaan Flutter untuk berpindah antar layar.",theSolution_en:"I created a simulated login and registration form using Flutter. This process involved implementing <code>TextEditingController</code> to capture inputs, adding built-in validation logic (such as checking for empty email or insufficient password length), and using Flutter's built-in <code>Navigator</code> system to transition between screens.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Form Validation",desc:"Validasi langsung di sisi klien untuk memastikan data terisi dengan format yang benar."},{title:"Routing Navigation",desc:"Perpindahan halaman (screen) yang mulus menggunakan Navigator Flutter."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Form Validation",desc:"Real-time client-side validation to ensure data is filled with the correct format."},{title:"Routing Navigation",desc:"Smooth transitions between screens using Flutter's Navigator."}],theImpact:"Aplikasi dasar ini menjadi <em>blueprint</em> atau fondasi bagi saya ketika harus membangun sistem autentikasi di aplikasi-aplikasi yang jauh lebih besar dan nyata di kemudian hari.",theImpact_en:"This basic application served as a <em>blueprint</em> and foundation for me when building authentication systems in much larger, real-world applications in the future."},a="/assets/dasar_flutter-DeYhyG7o.webp",w={title:"Kumpulan Dasar Flutter",title_en:"Basic Flutter Collection",slug:"kumpulan-dasar-flutter",isActive:!1,roles:["Mobile Developer"],roles_en:["Mobile Developer"],description:"Repositori latihan Flutter berisi berbagai eksperimen dasar seperti widget, layout, navigasi, dan manajemen state.",description_en:"A Flutter practice repository covering various basic topics such as widgets, layouts, navigation, and state management.",imageSrc:a,techTags:["Mobile App","Flutter","Dart","Layout","Widget"],timeline:"Dikerjakan waktu kuliah",timeline_en:"Developed during college",platform:"Mobile Application",platform_en:"Mobile Application",context:"Latihan & Pembelajaran",context_en:"Practice & Learning",projectUrl:"https://github.com/ariyoaziz/flutter",theChallenge:"Memasuki ekosistem Flutter membutuhkan pemahaman menyeluruh terhadap konsep <em>Widget</em>, di mana segala sesuatu di layar adalah Widget. Menghafal dan memahami ratusan widget bawaan Flutter tentu merupakan tugas yang memakan waktu.",theChallenge_en:"Entering the Flutter ecosystem requires a thorough understanding of the concept of <em>Widgets</em>, where everything on screen is a Widget. Memorizing and understanding hundreds of Flutter's built-in widgets is a time-consuming task.",theSolution:"Daripada menghafal, saya membuat repositori khusus ini sebagai 'buku catatan kode' (<em>code sandbox</em>) pribadi. Di sini saya secara aktif menulis dan mencoba berbagai widget, dari yang sederhana (Text, Container) hingga yang lebih kompleks (ListView, Stack).",theSolution_en:"Rather than memorizing, I created this dedicated repository as a personal 'code sandbox'. Here, I actively wrote and experimented with various widgets, from simple ones (Text, Container) to more complex ones (ListView, Stack).",keyFeatures:[{title:"Eksplorasi Widget",desc:"Implementasi praktis dari berbagai Widget inti Flutter."},{title:"Manajemen State Dasar",desc:"Pemahaman perbedaan antara StatelessWidget dan StatefulWidget."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Widget Exploration",desc:"Practical implementation of various core Flutter Widgets."},{title:"Basic State Management",desc:"Understanding the difference between StatelessWidget and StatefulWidget."}],theImpact:"Repositori ini bukan hanya melatih <em>muscle memory</em> saya dalam menulis kode Dart, tetapi juga sering saya jadikan bahan rujukan cepat (<em>cheatsheet</em>) saat sedang mengerjakan proyek mobile lainnya.",theImpact_en:"This repository not only trained my <em>muscle memory</em> in writing Dart code, but also frequently served as a quick reference cheatsheet while working on other mobile projects."},F="/assets/layout_flutter-PcUn6mok.webp",P={title:"Pemahaman Layout Flutter",title_en:"Flutter Layout Understanding",slug:"pemahaman-layout-flutter",isActive:!1,roles:["UI/UX Developer","Mobile Developer"],roles_en:["UI/UX Developer","Mobile Developer"],description:"Proyek latihan untuk memahami struktur layout Flutter seperti Row, Column, Stack, dan pengaturan posisi elemen.",description_en:"A practice project to understand layout structures in Flutter. Completed during the 5th semester to deepen interface design skills.",imageSrc:F,techTags:["Mobile App","Flutter","UI/UX Design"],timeline:"Dikerjakan waktu kuliah",timeline_en:"Developed during college",platform:"Mobile Application",platform_en:"Mobile Application",context:"Latihan Frontend Mobile",context_en:"Mobile Frontend Practice",projectUrl:"https://github.com/ariyoaziz/layout_apk",theChallenge:"Tantangan tersulit bagi pengembang baru di Flutter adalah memahami cara sistem layouting bekerja, mengingat Flutter tidak menggunakan CSS konvensional melainkan kombinasi Widget struktural seperti Row, Column, dan Flex.",theChallenge_en:"The most difficult challenge for new developers in Flutter is understanding how the layout system works, given that Flutter does not use conventional CSS but rather a combination of structural widgets like Row, Column, and Flex.",theSolution:"Saya membangun serangkaian antarmuka aplikasi dengan fokus sepenuhnya pada struktur layout. Saya banyak mengombinasikan penggunaan <code>Expanded</code>, <code>Flexible</code>, serta pengaturan alignment dan padding untuk memastikan tampilan UI tetap konsisten dan tidak mengalami <em>overflow</em> di berbagai ukuran layar HP.",theSolution_en:"I built a series of application interfaces focusing entirely on layout structure. I heavily combined the use of <code>Expanded</code>, <code>Flexible</code>, as well as alignment and padding settings to ensure the UI remains consistent and does not overflow on different mobile screen sizes.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Responsive Layouts",desc:"Pembuatan UI yang dinamis yang menyesuaikan diri dengan dimensi layar."},{title:"Complex Nesting",desc:"Latihan menumpuk (nesting) Row dan Column tanpa merusak struktur visual."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Responsive Layouts",desc:"Creating dynamic UIs that adapt to screen dimensions."},{title:"Complex Nesting",desc:"Exercises nesting Rows and Columns without breaking the visual structure."}],theImpact:"Proyek ini mematangkan kemampuan saya menerjemahkan desain (misal dari Figma) ke dalam kode Flutter dengan piksel yang akurat dan responsif.",theImpact_en:"This project matured my ability to translate designs (e.g., from Figma) into Flutter code with pixel-perfect accuracy and responsiveness."},_={title:"Dasar Framework Flutter",title_en:"Basic Flutter Framework",slug:"dasar-framework-flutter",isActive:!1,roles:["Mahasiswa","Mobile Developer"],roles_en:["Student","Mobile Developer"],description:"Aplikasi latihan untuk memahami konsep dasar framework Flutter yang dikerjakan pada mata kuliah Dasar Framework semester 5.",description_en:"A simple practice app to understand the core concepts of the Flutter framework. Developed for the Basic Framework course (5th semester).",imageSrc:a,techTags:["Mobile App","Flutter","Dart"],timeline:"Dikerjakan waktu kuliah (Semester 5)",timeline_en:"Developed during college (5th Semester)",platform:"Mobile Application",platform_en:"Mobile Application",context:"Tugas Mata Kuliah",context_en:"Academic Coursework",projectUrl:"https://github.com/ariyoaziz/dasar_framework_flutter",theChallenge:"Sebagai bagian dari kurikulum akademik di semester 5, saya ditugaskan untuk membuat sebuah aplikasi mandiri yang bisa merepresentasikan pemahaman mendalam tentang teori dan praktik dasar pembuatan aplikasi mobile menggunakan framework Flutter.",theChallenge_en:"As part of the academic curriculum in the 5th semester, I was tasked with creating an independent application that could represent a deep understanding of the theory and basic practice of mobile application development using the Flutter framework.",theSolution:"Saya menyusun aplikasi mobile sederhana yang merangkum berbagai modul pembelajaran kampus. Kode disusun serapi mungkin mengikuti standar penulisan (<em>best practice</em>) agar mudah dinilai dan dipahami oleh dosen serta rekan mahasiswa lainnya.",theSolution_en:"I assembled a simple mobile application summarizing various campus learning modules. The code was structured as neatly as possible following best practices to be easily evaluated and understood by lecturers and fellow students.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Penerapan Teori",desc:"Mengubah modul teori di kelas menjadi aplikasi berjalan yang fungsional."},{title:"Modular Code",desc:"Penulisan kode Dart yang rapi dan terstruktur dalam bentuk fungsi dan kelas."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Theoretical Application",desc:"Converting classroom theoretical modules into a functional, running application."},{title:"Modular Code",desc:"Neat and structured Dart code written in the form of functions and classes."}],theImpact:"Selain berhasil memenuhi syarat kelulusan mata kuliah dengan nilai memuaskan, proyek ini menumbuhkan rasa percaya diri saya untuk mulai mengambil proyek pengembangan aplikasi mobile di luar lingkup kampus.",theImpact_en:"Besides successfully completing the course requirements with satisfactory grades, this project built my confidence to start taking on mobile application development projects outside the university scope."},I="/assets/linkaja-BOdbDh29.webp",A={title:"UI/UX Redesign – Aplikasi LinkAja (Halaman Beranda)",title_en:"UI/UX Redesign – LinkAja App (Homepage)",slug:"ui-ux-redesign-aplikasi-linkaja-halaman-beranda",isActive:!1,roles:["UI/UX Designer"],roles_en:["UI/UX Designer"],description:"Redesain halaman beranda aplikasi LinkAja dengan fokus pada penyederhanaan antarmuka dan peningkatan navigasi pengguna.",description_en:"Redesign of the LinkAja app homepage focusing on interface simplification, logical feature grouping, and improved visual accessibility. Features a modern and clean style for better mobile navigation.",imageSrc:I,techTags:["UI/UX Design","Figma","Redesign","Mobile App"],timeline:"Dikerjakan waktu kuliah",timeline_en:"Developed during college",platform:"Design Concept / Figma",platform_en:"Design Concept / Figma",context:"Studi Kasus UI/UX",context_en:"UI/UX Case Study",projectUrl:"https://www.figma.com/proto/IDGtCHDIcpBGVSCdmmEieC/Desain-Ulang-APP-LInkAja?page-id=5%3A57&node-id=5-60&p=f&viewport=293%2C-18%2C1.28&t=tBMct1pVLikWEzHC-1&scaling=scale-down&content-scaling=fixed",theChallenge:"Aplikasi keuangan digital seringkali dipenuhi dengan puluhan fitur dan ikon promosi di halaman berandanya, membuat pengguna baru merasa kebingungan (<em>cognitive overload</em>) saat mencoba mencari fitur utama seperti transfer atau pembayaran.",theChallenge_en:"Digital financial apps are often packed with dozens of features and promotional icons on their homepage, causing new users to experience cognitive overload when trying to find main functions like transfers or payments.",theSolution:"Melalui proses riset desain, saya merancang ulang halaman beranda LinkAja di Figma. Saya mengelompokkan ikon berdasarkan kategori prioritas, memperbesar elemen navigasi utama, serta memberikan ruang kosong (<em>white space</em>) yang cukup agar tampilan terasa lebih bersih, modern, dan minimalis.",theSolution_en:"Through a design research process, I redesigned the LinkAja homepage in Figma. I grouped icons based on priority categories, enlarged the main navigation elements, and provided sufficient white space so that the layout feels cleaner, more modern, and minimalist.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Simplified Navigation",desc:"Mengurangi kekacauan visual dengan memprioritaskan fungsi utama aplikasi."},{title:"Modern Aesthetics",desc:"Pendekatan warna dan tipografi baru yang lebih menyegarkan mata pengguna."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Simplified Navigation",desc:"Reduces visual clutter by prioritizing the app's core functionalities."},{title:"Modern Aesthetics",desc:"A refreshing new color and typography approach that is easier on the user's eyes."}],theImpact:"Desain ulang ini menghasilkan prototipe visual yang jauh lebih intuitif. Studi kasus ini membuktikan bahwa penyederhanaan antarmuka dapat secara drastis meningkatkan kenyamanan pengguna tanpa harus menghilangkan fungsionalitas bisnis dari aplikasi itu sendiri.",theImpact_en:"This redesign resulted in a significantly more intuitive visual prototype. This case study demonstrates that simplifying the interface can drastically improve user comfort without eliminating the business functionalities of the app itself."},S="/assets/oop_musiksederhana-D0dedYtP.webp",j={title:"CLI Pemutar Musik Sederhana",title_en:"Simple CLI Music Player",slug:"cli-pemutar-musik-sederhana",isActive:!1,roles:["Backend Developer"],roles_en:["Backend Developer"],description:"Aplikasi pemutar musik berbasis command line menggunakan Python dengan konsep pemrograman berorientasi objek.",description_en:"A CLI-based music player app using Python. A group project for the Object-Oriented Programming course (3rd semester).",imageSrc:S,techTags:["Backend","Python","CLI","Object-Oriented Programming"],timeline:"Dikerjakan waktu kuliah",timeline_en:"Developed during college",platform:"Command Line / Terminal",platform_en:"Command Line / Terminal",context:"Tugas OOP Python",context_en:"Python OOP Assignment",projectUrl:"https://github.com/ariyoaziz/oop-pemutar-musik-sederhana",theChallenge:"Mempelajari paradigma <em>Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)</em> seringkali terasa abstrak jika hanya lewat teori. Tantangannya adalah mengimplementasikan pilar OOP (Class, Inheritance, Encapsulation, Polymorphism) ke dalam sebuah program yang logikanya nyata dan mudah dipahami.",theChallenge_en:"Learning the <em>Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)</em> paradigm often feels abstract through theory alone. The challenge was to implement OOP pillars (Class, Inheritance, Encapsulation, Polymorphism) into a program with concrete, easily understandable logic.",theSolution:"Saya memilih untuk membangun program pemutar musik berbasis terminal (CLI) menggunakan Python. Di dalam sistem, entitas seperti <code>Lagu</code>, <code>Playlist</code>, dan <code>Pemutar</code> direpresentasikan sebagai objek yang saling berinteraksi. Pengguna dapat mengetikkan perintah untuk memutar lagu, melewati (<em>skip</em>), atau mengacak daftar putar.",theSolution_en:"I chose to build a terminal-based (CLI) music player program using Python. Inside the system, entities such as <code>Song</code>, <code>Playlist</code>, and <code>Player</code> are represented as objects interacting with each other. Users can type commands to play, skip, or shuffle the playlist.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Penerapan OOP Murni",desc:"Arsitektur kode berbasis objek yang memudahkan penambahan fitur di kemudian hari."},{title:"Interactive CLI",desc:"Antarmuka terminal interaktif untuk mengontrol pemutaran musik virtual."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Pure OOP Application",desc:"Object-based code architecture making it easy to add features in the future."},{title:"Interactive CLI",desc:"Interactive terminal interface to control virtual music playback."}],theImpact:"Melalui pembuatan program ini, pemahaman konseptual saya mengenai OOP menjadi sangat solid. Kode menjadi jauh lebih rapi, modular, dan lebih mudah dilacak kerusakannya (<em>debug</em>) berkat pemisahan tanggung jawab pada masing-masing Class.",theImpact_en:"By creating this program, my conceptual understanding of OOP became highly solid. The code is much cleaner, modular, and easier to debug thanks to the separation of concerns across classes."},D="/assets/web_peminjaman-CognzN1E.webp",C={title:"Sistem Peminjaman Uang Web",title_en:"Web Loan System",slug:"sistem-peminjaman-uang-web",isActive:!1,roles:["Fullstack Developer","UI/UX Designer"],roles_en:["Fullstack Developer","UI/UX Designer"],description:"Aplikasi web peminjaman uang menggunakan Flask dan MySQL dengan fitur manajemen pengguna dan pencatatan transaksi.",description_en:"A web-based money borrowing application built with Flask and MySQL. Created as a group in the Practical Web Programming course (3rd semester).",imageSrc:D,techTags:["Web App","Flask","Python","MySQL","UI/UX Design"],timeline:"Dikerjakan waktu kuliah",timeline_en:"Developed during college",platform:"Web Application",platform_en:"Web Application",context:"Sistem Informasi Manajemen",context_en:"Management Information System Assignment",projectUrl:"https://github.com/ariyoaziz/web_peminjaman",theChallenge:"Sistem pencatatan utang atau peminjaman uang yang manual rentan terhadap hilangnya data dan perselisihan jumlah. Tantangannya adalah menciptakan aplikasi pencatatan digital yang andal untuk menyimpan riwayat peminjaman dengan relasi database yang terstruktur.",theChallenge_en:"Manual recording systems for loans and debt calculations are highly prone to data loss and amount disputes. The challenge was to create a reliable digital ledger application to store loan history with structured database relationships.",theSolution:"Aplikasi ini dibangun menggunakan arsitektur web lengkap: <strong>Flask (Python)</strong> sebagai otak aplikasi (backend) dan <strong>MySQL</strong> sebagai tempat penyimpanan (database). Sistem ini mengatur relasi antara data Pengguna, Transaksi, dan Status Pembayaran sehingga riwayat utang tercatat dengan rapi dan aman.",theSolution_en:"This application was built using a complete web architecture: <strong>Flask (Python)</strong> as the application backend and <strong>MySQL</strong> as the database storage. The system orchestrates relationships between User, Transaction, and Payment Status data so that debt history is logged cleanly and securely.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Manajemen Database Relasional",desc:"Penyimpanan data transaksi berbasis MySQL dengan struktur tabel terintegrasi."},{title:"Pencatatan Transaksi",desc:"Laporan keluar masuk peminjaman yang bisa dilihat kembali secara historis."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Relational Database Management",desc:"MySQL-based transaction data storage with integrated table structures."},{title:"Transaction Ledger",desc:"Incoming and outgoing loan logs that can be historically reviewed."}],theImpact:"Proyek sistem informasi ini melatih kemampuan <em>full-stack</em> saya, mulai dari merancang skema database (ERD), membangun rute API dengan Flask, hingga menampilkannya di antarmuka web, membuktikan kesiapan dalam membangun aplikasi pendataan bisnis skala kecil.",theImpact_en:"This information system project trained my <em>full-stack</em> skills, from designing database schemas (ERD) and building API routes with Flask, to rendering them on the web interface, proving my readiness to build small-scale business data systems."},U="/assets/tanpa-batas-Ci9zTXql.webp",M={title:"Pameran Foto – Tanpa Batas",title_en:"Photography Exhibition – Tanpa Batas",slug:"pameran-foto-tanpa-batas",isActive:!1,roles:["Photographer","Exhibitor"],roles_en:["Photographer","Exhibitor"],description:"Karya fotografi bertema eksplorasi imajinasi yang dipamerkan dalam event fotografi Tanpa Batas tahun 2024.",description_en:"Photography work themed around exploring imagination exhibited in the 'Tanpa Batas' event in 2024.",imageSrc:U,techTags:["Photography","Event","Exhibition"],timeline:"2024",timeline_en:"2024",platform:"Exhibition / Physical",platform_en:"Exhibition / Physical",context:"Karya Pameran Fotografi",context_en:"Photography Exhibition Work",projectUrl:"https://www.instagram.com/p/C7LNeYthrUm/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&igsh=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==",theChallenge:"Menghadirkan karya seni visual yang tidak terikat oleh realitas. Tantangannya adalah menstimulasi audiens untuk berpikir di luar batas logika normal dan melihat kebebasan imajinasi murni melalui medium lensa kamera.",theChallenge_en:"Presenting visual artwork that is not bound by reality. The challenge was to stimulate the audience to think outside the limits of normal logic and witness pure imaginative freedom through the camera lens.",theSolution:"Saya bereksperimen dengan berbagai teknik komposisi tidak lazim, pencahayaan dramatis, dan permainan distorsi perspektif. Karya-karya ini dipilih secara kuratif untuk memberikan ruang bagi audiens dalam menginterpretasikan maknanya masing-masing, menciptakan diskusi dua arah antara karya dan penikmatnya.",theSolution_en:"I experimented with various unconventional composition techniques, dramatic lighting, and perspective distortion. These works were curatively selected to give the audience space to interpret their own meanings, creating a two-way discussion between the artwork and the viewer.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Konsep Surealisme",desc:"Pendekatan visual yang mencoba mendobrak batasan realitas fisik."},{title:"Interaksi Audiens",desc:"Karya yang secara khusus dirancang untuk memicu pertanyaan dan interpretasi bebas."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Surrealist Concept",desc:"A visual approach attempting to break through the boundaries of physical reality."},{title:"Audience Interaction",desc:"Artwork specifically designed to trigger questions and open interpretations."}],theImpact:"Menjadi salah satu karya yang disorot dalam pameran <strong>Tanpa Batas 2024</strong>. Respons audiens sangat beragam, membuktikan bahwa fotografi mampu melampaui dokumentasi belaka dan menjadi alat ekspresi ideologi yang kuat.",theImpact_en:"Became one of the highlighted works in the <strong>Tanpa Batas 2024</strong> exhibition. Audience responses were diverse, proving that photography can transcend mere documentation and become a powerful tool for ideological expression."},T="/assets/oop_pengirimanbarang-CBeu3-s7.webp",x={title:"CLI Simulasi Pengiriman",title_en:"CLI Shipping Simulation",slug:"cli-simulasi-pengiriman",isActive:!1,roles:["Backend Developer"],roles_en:["Backend Developer"],description:"Aplikasi simulasi layanan pengiriman barang berbasis command line menggunakan Python.",description_en:"A CLI-based shipping service simulation app using Python. A group project for the OOP course (3rd semester).",imageSrc:T,techTags:["Backend","Python","CLI","Object-Oriented Programming"],timeline:"Dikerjakan waktu kuliah",timeline_en:"Developed during college",platform:"Command Line / Terminal",platform_en:"Command Line / Terminal",context:"Tugas Pemrograman Berorientasi Objek",context_en:"Object-Oriented Programming Assignment",projectUrl:"https://github.com/ariyoaziz/oop-layanan-pengiriman",theChallenge:"Memodelkan alur logistik logistik di dunia nyata—seperti pengumpulan paket, pemilihan kurir, penghitungan ongkos, dan rute pengiriman—ke dalam bahasa pemrograman menggunakan logika berbasis objek (OOP).",theChallenge_en:"Modeling real-world logistics workflows—such as package collection, courier assignment, shipping cost calculation, and delivery routes—into a programming language using object-oriented (OOP) logic.",theSolution:"Sistem CLI ini dikembangkan dengan membagi peran-peran tersebut ke dalam <em>Class</em> Python. Ada Class untuk <code>Paket</code> (yang menyimpan dimensi dan berat), <code>Kurir</code>, dan <code>SistemEkspedisi</code>. Pengguna terminal bisa mensimulasikan proses dari pendaftaran paket hingga paket dinyatakan terkirim.",theSolution_en:"This CLI system was developed by dividing those roles into Python <em>classes</em>. There are classes for <code>Package</code> (storing dimensions and weight), <code>Courier</code>, and <code>ExpeditionSystem</code>. Terminal users can simulate the process from registering a package until it is declared delivered.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Simulasi Logistik",desc:"Penghitungan biaya pengiriman secara otomatis berdasarkan berat dan jarak."},{title:"Struktur Class Dinamis",desc:"Penggunaan pewarisan (inheritance) untuk mengklasifikasikan jenis layanan pengiriman (Reguler, Kilat)."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Logistics Simulation",desc:"Automatic shipping cost calculation based on weight and distance."},{title:"Dynamic Class Structure",desc:"Use of inheritance to classify types of shipping services (Regular, Express)."}],theImpact:"Proyek ini melatih nalar algoritmik saya dalam memecahkan proses bisnis nyata ke dalam barisan kode terstruktur, memperkuat pemahaman mendalam tentang prinsip desain software (<em>Software Design Principles</em>).",theImpact_en:"This project sharpened my algorithmic reasoning in translating real-world business processes into structured code lines, reinforcing a deep understanding of software design principles."},W="/assets/rona-cPwmJ1u1.webp",L={title:"Pameran Diksar – Rona",title_en:"Diksar Exhibition – Rona",slug:"pameran-diksar-rona",isActive:!1,roles:["Photographer"],roles_en:["Photographer"],description:"Karya fotografi yang dipamerkan dalam pameran Rona sebagai bagian dari pendidikan dasar organisasi fotografi tahun 2023.",description_en:"Photography work displayed in the 'Rona' exhibition as part of a basic photography organization training in 2023.",imageSrc:W,techTags:["Photography","Event","Exhibition"],timeline:"2023",timeline_en:"2023",platform:"Exhibition / Physical",platform_en:"Exhibition / Physical",context:"Pendidikan Dasar Fotografi",context_en:"Basic Photography Training",projectUrl:"#",theChallenge:"Sebagai seorang pemula yang baru mendalami ilmu fotografi di tingkat pendidikan dasar organisasi, tantangan terbesarnya adalah menemukan ciri khas (<em>style</em>) dan keberanian berekspresi melalui komposisi warna, emosi, dan elemen pencahayaan.",theChallenge_en:"As a beginner newly diving into photography during the organization's basic education, the greatest challenge was finding a unique style and the courage to express it through color composition, emotion, and lighting elements.",theSolution:"Saya memfokuskan lensa pada permainan warna-warna kontras dan interaksi manusia dengan lingkungannya. Melalui proses kurasi yang ketat dan bimbingan mentor, foto ini terpilih karena dianggap berhasil menyampaikan cerita visual tanpa harus bergantung pada keterangan teks.",theSolution_en:"I focused my lens on contrasting colors and human interaction with their environment. Through a strict curation process and guidance from mentors, this photo was selected because it successfully conveyed a visual story without relying on text descriptions.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Komposisi Warna",desc:"Pemanfaatan kontras warna terang dan gelap untuk menonjolkan subjek."},{title:"Visual Storytelling",desc:"Menangkap momen sekilas (candid) yang bercerita."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Color Composition",desc:"Utilization of contrast between bright and dark colors to highlight the subject."},{title:"Visual Storytelling",desc:"Capturing a candid, narrative-driven fleeting moment."}],theImpact:"Karya ini menjadi batu pijakan pertama saya di dunia fotografi formal. Dipamerkan di hadapan publik memberikan rasa percaya diri serta masukan berharga yang membentuk cara pandang estetika visual saya saat ini.",theImpact_en:"This work was my first stepping stone in formal photography. Being exhibited in front of the public gave me confidence as well as valuable feedback that shaped my current perspective on visual aesthetics."},O="/assets/estetika_kopi-CQJMb4mC.webp",B={title:"Website Estetika Kopi",title_en:"Estetika Kopi Website",slug:"website-estetika-kopi",isActive:!1,roles:["Fullstack Developer"],roles_en:["Fullstack Developer"],description:"Website untuk kedai kopi dengan fokus pada tampilan visual estetis dan pengalaman pengguna yang menarik.",description_en:"A coffee shop website focusing on visual aesthetics and user experience. Built with CodeIgniter 4 and PHP.",imageSrc:O,techTags:["Web App","Frontend","CodeIgniter 4","PHP"],timeline:"Dikerjakan waktu kuliah",timeline_en:"Developed during college",platform:"Web Application",platform_en:"Web Application",context:"Tugas Pemrograman Web",context_en:"Web Programming Assignment",projectUrl:"https://github.com/ariyoaziz/pemrograman_web-estetika.kopi-",theChallenge:"Membuat website bisnis (kedai kopi) yang tidak hanya berfungsi menampilkan menu, tetapi juga mampu memancarkan identitas visual <em>brand</em> secara estetis, layaknya mengunjungi kedai kopi yang modern dan nyaman secara langsung.",theChallenge_en:"Creating a business website (coffee shop) that not only functions to display the menu, but is also capable of aesthetically reflecting the brand's visual identity, much like visiting a modern and cozy coffee shop in person.",theSolution:"Aplikasi ini dirancang menggunakan arsitektur MVC (Model-View-Controller) dengan <strong>CodeIgniter 4</strong> (PHP). Sisi antarmuka (<em>frontend</em>) saya bangun dengan kombinasi CSS kustom dan <em>assets</em> berkualitas tinggi untuk menonjolkan sisi estetika, sementara pengelolaan rute dan data produk dikendalikan oleh backend CI4.",theSolution_en:"This application was designed using the MVC (Model-View-Controller) architecture with <strong>CodeIgniter 4</strong> (PHP). The frontend interface was built combining custom CSS and high-quality assets to highlight the aesthetic aspect, while route management and product data are handled by the CI4 backend.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Product Showcase",desc:"Tampilan galeri menu kopi yang interaktif dan menggugah selera."},{title:"Arsitektur MVC",desc:"Penulisan struktur kode PHP modern yang mudah di-maintain."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Product Showcase",desc:"Interactive and appetizing menu gallery display."},{title:"MVC Architecture",desc:"Writing modern PHP code structure that is easy to maintain."}],theImpact:"Website ini berhasil memenuhi ekspektasi desain sebuah <em>company profile</em> FnB (Food and Beverages) sekaligus memperkuat kemampuan saya dalam menggunakan framework CodeIgniter 4 dalam pengembangan backend.",theImpact_en:"This website successfully met the design expectations of an FnB (Food and Beverages) company profile while reinforcing my skills in utilizing the CodeIgniter 4 framework for backend development."},z="/assets/e-com-D4MADJYd.webp",E={title:"UI/UX Design – Website E-Commerce Alat Outdoor",title_en:"UI/UX Design – Outdoor Gear E-Commerce",slug:"ui-ux-design-website-e-commerce-alat-outdoor",isActive:!1,roles:["UI/UX Designer"],roles_en:["UI/UX Designer"],description:"Desain UI/UX untuk platform e-commerce perlengkapan outdoor dengan navigasi yang intuitif dan visual yang bersih.",description_en:"Interface design for an e-commerce platform selling outdoor gear such as tents, cooking equipment, and hiking clothes. Focuses on intuitive user experience.",imageSrc:z,techTags:["UI/UX Design","Figma","E-Commerce","Prototyping"],timeline:"Dikerjakan waktu kuliah",timeline_en:"Developed during college",platform:"Design Concept / Figma",platform_en:"Design Concept / Figma",context:"Latihan Eksplorasi Desain",context_en:"Design Exploration Practice",projectUrl:"https://www.figma.com/design/cQTRvW7zsCFRTWT30f5tHe/e-Com?node-id=0-1&t=kskOzYVPNCdrkweR-1",theChallenge:"Situs <em>e-commerce</em> seringkali penuh sesak dengan produk, filter, dan promosi yang membuat pengguna kebingungan mencari barang spesifik, terutama untuk produk <em>niche</em> seperti peralatan <em>outdoor</em> dan <em>hiking</em>.",theChallenge_en:"E-commerce websites are often cluttered with products, filters, and promotions that confuse users looking for specific items, especially for niche products like outdoor and hiking gear.",theSolution:"Saya memusatkan desain pada navigasi yang efisien (<em>frictionless navigation</em>). Proses penyaringan kategori (tenda, alat masak, pakaian) dibuat sangat menonjol. Saya menerapkan skema warna <em>earth-tone</em> yang selaras dengan tema alam bebas, serta memberikan ruang kosong yang luas (<em>clean UI</em>) di sekitar foto produk.",theSolution_en:"I focused the design on frictionless navigation. The category filtering process (tents, cooking gear, apparel) is highly emphasized. I applied an earth-toned color palette aligned with the outdoor theme, and provided ample white space around product photos for a clean UI.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Clean Layout",desc:"Fokus langsung pada produk berkualitas tinggi tanpa distraksi elemen berlebih."},{title:"Intuitive Filtering",desc:"Sistem filter dan pencarian yang disesuaikan dengan kebiasaan pendaki/petualang."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Clean Layout",desc:"Direct focus on high-quality products without the distraction of excessive UI elements."},{title:"Intuitive Filtering",desc:"Filter and search systems customized to the habits of hikers/adventurers."}],theImpact:"Menghasilkan <em>mockup</em> UI beresolusi tinggi yang siap diserahkan (<em>hand-off</em>) kepada tim <em>frontend</em>. Desain ini membuktikan kemampuan saya merangkai antarmuka penjualan yang berorientasi pada konversi (<em>conversion-centric design</em>).",theImpact_en:"Delivered a high-fidelity UI mockup ready for hand-off to the frontend team. This design demonstrates my ability to create sales interfaces focused on conversion-centric design."},R="/assets/food-order-BvjOOP68.webp",K={title:"UI/UX Design – Order Food App",title_en:"UI/UX Design – Order Food App",slug:"ui-ux-design-order-food-app",isActive:!1,roles:["UI/UX Designer"],roles_en:["UI/UX Designer"],description:"Konsep desain aplikasi pemesanan makanan dengan tampilan modern dan alur pemesanan yang sederhana.",description_en:"Food ordering app design concept with a clean and modern approach. Provides an easily navigable user experience.",imageSrc:R,techTags:["UI/UX Design","Figma","Mobile App","Prototype"],timeline:"Dikerjakan waktu kuliah",timeline_en:"Developed during college",platform:"Design Concept / Figma",platform_en:"Design Concept / Figma",context:"Personal Portfolio Design",context_en:"Personal Portfolio Design",projectUrl:"https://www.behance.net/gallery/210655317/order-food",theChallenge:"Membuat aplikasi pengantaran makanan mengharuskan kita memikirkan bagaimana pengguna bisa menemukan makanan favorit, memasukkan ke keranjang, dan melakukan <em>checkout</em> dalam jumlah ketukan (<em>taps</em>) seminimal mungkin.",theChallenge_en:"Creating a food delivery app requires thinking about how users can find their favorite food, add it to the cart, and complete checkout in as few taps as possible.",theSolution:"Desain aplikasi ini memprioritaskan fotografi makanan (<em>food imagery</em>) yang besar untuk menggugah selera pengguna. Alur pemesanan dirancang secara linier (satu arah) agar tidak membingungkan, dari halaman beranda, rincian menu, modifikasi pesanan (<em>add-ons</em>), hingga layar <em>checkout</em> akhir.",theSolution_en:"The design of this application prioritizes large food imagery to stimulate the user's appetite. The order flow is designed linearly (one-way) to avoid confusion, navigating smoothly from the homepage, menu details, order customizations (add-ons), to the final checkout screen.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Appetizing Visuals",desc:"Penataan UI yang menonjolkan visual gambar menu dengan tata letak bergaya modern."},{title:"Linear Checkout Flow",desc:"Alur pembelian yang sangat ringkas untuk mempercepat proses konversi pesanan."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Appetizing Visuals",desc:"UI layout highlighting menu imagery with modern layout styles."},{title:"Linear Checkout Flow",desc:"A highly simplified buying flow to speed up the order conversion process."}],theImpact:"Konsep desain ini telah dipublikasikan di Behance dan mendapatkan apresiasi positif atas pendekatan minimalisnya yang tetap mempertahankan fungsionalitas utama aplikasi pesan antar.",theImpact_en:"This design concept was published on Behance and received positive feedback for its minimalist approach while retaining the core features of a food delivery application."},V="/assets/kopi-C3v7gSjj.webp",X={title:"UI/UX Design – Coffee App",title_en:"UI/UX Design – Coffee App",slug:"ui-ux-design-coffee-app",isActive:!1,roles:["UI/UX Designer"],roles_en:["UI/UX Designer"],description:"Desain antarmuka aplikasi pemesanan kopi dengan visual elegan dan alur pengguna yang sederhana.",description_en:"An elegant and modern coffee ordering app interface design, emphasizing user comfort. Designed using Figma.",imageSrc:V,techTags:["UI/UX Design","Figma","Mobile App","Product Design"],timeline:"Dikerjakan waktu kuliah",timeline_en:"Developed during college",platform:"Design Concept / Figma",platform_en:"Design Concept / Figma",context:"Personal Portfolio Design",context_en:"Personal Portfolio Design",projectUrl:"https://www.behance.net/gallery/210655381/coffee",theChallenge:"Aplikasi <em>coffee shop</em> membutuhkan sentuhan personalisasi yang kuat (seperti mengatur ukuran gelas, kadar gula, jenis susu, dan es) tanpa membuat tampilan pemesanan terasa mengintimidasi atau rumit layaknya formulir panjang.",theChallenge_en:"Coffee shop applications require a strong touch of personalization (such as adjusting cup sizes, sweetness, milk types, and ice) without making the ordering screen feel intimidating or cluttered like a long form.",theSolution:"Saya memecahkan masalah ini dengan pendekatan <em>card UI</em> dan <em>toggle buttons</em>. Pengguna dapat meracik kopi mereka melalui opsi visual yang menyenangkan secara interaktif. Skema warna yang digunakan didominasi oleh corak kopi elegan dan gaya minimalis yang mewah (<em>premium feel</em>).",theSolution_en:"I solved this problem using a card UI and toggle button approach. Users can customize their drinks interactively through pleasant visual choices. The color palette is dominated by elegant coffee shades and a luxurious minimalist styling for a premium feel.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Customization Interface",desc:"Antarmuka kustomisasi minuman (gula, es, susu) yang sangat mudah digunakan."},{title:"Premium Dark Theme",desc:"Skema warna elegan yang mencerminkan suasana kedai kopi berkelas."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Customization Interface",desc:"Highly intuitive drink customization interface (sugar, ice, milk) with minimal steps."},{title:"Premium Dark Theme",desc:"An elegant color scheme reflecting the atmosphere of a classy coffee shop."}],theImpact:"Desain ini (yang juga dapat dilihat di portofolio Behance saya) merepresentasikan kapabilitas saya dalam memadukan keindahan visual estetis dengan pengalaman pengguna (<em>User Experience</em>) yang logis dan fungsional.",theImpact_en:"This design (which is also showcased on my Behance portfolio) represents my capability to blend aesthetic visual beauty with a logical, functional User Experience."},H="/assets/dapur-vanny-C_NDzQFV.png",q={title:"Dapur Vanny – Website Katalog UMKM Kuliner",title_en:"Dapur Vanny – Culinary MSME Catalog Website",slug:"dapur-vanny-website-katalog-umkm-kuliner",isActive:!0,roles:["UI/UX Designer","Frontend Developer"],roles_en:["UI/UX Designer","Frontend Developer"],description:"Website katalog produk UMKM kuliner (jajan pasar & snack box) yang responsif, ramah pengguna, dan optimal di desktop maupun mobile, lengkap dengan halaman produk dan formulir pemesanan.",description_en:"A responsive and user-friendly product catalog website for a culinary MSME (traditional snacks & snack boxes), optimized for both desktop and mobile, featuring a product page and order form.",imageSrc:H,techTags:["HTML","CSS","JavaScript","Vercel","UI/UX Design"],timeline:"2025",timeline_en:"2025",platform:"Website (Responsive)",platform_en:"Website (Responsive)",context:"Proyek Klien / UMKM",context_en:"Client Project / MSME",projectUrl:"https://dapur-vanny.vercel.app/",theChallenge:"Dapur Vanny, sebuah UMKM kuliner yang bergerak di bidang jajan pasar dan snack box, belum memiliki kehadiran digital yang memadai. Pelanggan yang ingin melihat daftar menu, harga, dan cara memesan seringkali harus bertanya melalui chat—proses yang tidak efisien dan berpotensi kehilangan calon pembeli. Tantangannya adalah membangun sebuah <strong>etalase digital</strong> yang bisa diakses kapan saja, dengan antarmuka yang ramah bagi segmen pelanggan yang beragam mulai dari ibu rumah tangga hingga pelaku event.",theChallenge_en:"Dapur Vanny, a culinary MSME specializing in traditional snacks and snack boxes, lacked a proper digital presence. Customers who wanted to view the menu, prices, and ordering process had to ask via chat—an inefficient process that risked losing potential buyers. The challenge was to build a <strong>digital storefront</strong> accessible at any time, with an interface friendly for a diverse customer base ranging from homemakers to event organizers.",theSolution:"Saya merancang dan mengembangkan website katalog produk end-to-end menggunakan HTML, CSS, dan JavaScript murni, di-deploy di Vercel untuk performa dan keandalan tinggi. Desain diprioritaskan pada <strong>kemudahan navigasi</strong>: hierarki informasi yang jelas, kategori produk yang terstruktur (Menu, Makanan Kering, Paket Acara), dan ajakan bertindak (CTA) yang menonjol. Formulir pemesanan diintegrasikan langsung dengan <strong>WhatsApp</strong>, menyederhanakan alur konversi menjadi satu klik bagi pelanggan.",theSolution_en:"I designed and developed the product catalog website end-to-end using plain HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, deployed on Vercel for high performance and reliability. The design was prioritized around <strong>ease of navigation</strong>: a clear information hierarchy, structured product categories (Menu, Dry Foods, Event Packages), and prominent calls-to-action (CTAs). The order form is directly integrated with <strong>WhatsApp</strong>, simplifying the conversion flow to a single click for customers.",keyFeatures:[{title:"Katalog Produk Terstruktur",desc:"Halaman menu yang terorganisir dengan kategori jelas: jajan pasar, makanan kering, dan paket acara, memudahkan pelanggan menemukan produk yang diinginkan."},{title:"Formulir Pemesanan via WhatsApp",desc:"Integrasi langsung dengan WhatsApp memungkinkan pelanggan melakukan pemesanan dengan satu klik, mempersingkat alur konversi secara signifikan."},{title:"Desain Responsif Mobile-First",desc:"Tampilan yang optimal di semua ukuran layar—dari smartphone hingga desktop—memastikan pengalaman belanja yang nyaman bagi semua pelanggan."},{title:"Informasi Cara Pesan yang Jelas",desc:"Halaman khusus yang menjelaskan langkah-langkah pemesanan secara ringkas, mengurangi kebingungan dan meningkatkan kepercayaan calon pembeli."}],keyFeatures_en:[{title:"Structured Product Catalog",desc:"A well-organized menu page with clear categories—traditional snacks, dry foods, and event packages—making it easy for customers to find what they need."},{title:"WhatsApp Order Form",desc:"Direct WhatsApp integration lets customers place orders in one click, significantly shortening the conversion flow."},{title:"Mobile-First Responsive Design",desc:"Optimized display across all screen sizes—from smartphones to desktops—ensuring a comfortable shopping experience for every customer."},{title:"Clear Order Instructions Page",desc:"A dedicated page explaining the ordering steps concisely, reducing confusion and building trust with potential buyers."}],theImpact:"Website berhasil memberikan Dapur Vanny sebuah <strong>etalase digital profesional</strong> yang bekerja 24/7 tanpa bergantung pada pesan chat manual. Desain yang berfokus pada konversi dan navigasi yang intuitif berhasil menyederhanakan proses pemesanan bagi pelanggan, meningkatkan efisiensi operasional UMKM, dan memperluas jangkauan pasar di luar jaringan kontak langsung.",theImpact_en:"The website successfully gave Dapur Vanny a <strong>professional digital storefront</strong> that works 24/7 without relying on manual chat messages. The conversion-focused design and intuitive navigation successfully simplified the ordering process for customers, improved MSME operational efficiency, and expanded market reach beyond their direct contact network."},N=[n,t,r,l,q,d,u,c,k,y,v,w,P,_,A,j,C,M,x,L,B,E,K,X],Q=N,G=[{name:"Programmer",active:!0},{name:"UI/UX",active:!1},{name:"Photography",active:!1}];export{G as i,Q as p};
